Okay, Sri Lanka.

50
00:02:18,500 --> 00:02:24,060
Actually, you say drafted, he joined of his
own accord in the 1920s.

51
00:02:24,060 --> 00:02:27,670
Mainly because there weren’t enough things
to cut up in Ceylon!

52
00:02:27,670 --> 00:02:30,550
Well, yes, he left the army in 1936.

53
00:02:30,550 --> 00:02:32,760
Because there was not enough fighting.

54
