He then worked as a few other things.

55
00:02:35,830 --> 00:02:37,080
What might that be?

56
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:40,300
One is a phrase I wouldn’t associate with
the 1930s,

57
00:02:40,300 --> 00:02:43,210
